(284, 5, NULL, 0, 'Pier Wall Hung WC & Soft Close Seat', NULL, 'Small bathrooms no longer have to compromise when it comes to great design and first-class function. The Pier WC, a contemporary yet very simple toilet, has the shortest projection on the market at a minimal 43cm.\r\n\r\nNot only compact, the seat is still extremely comfortable and fits perfectly in limited spaces, whilst the high-function flush performance is as good as it gets.Introducing an innovation in ceramic glaze technology, Pier is expertly crafted from CERASLIDE®; a forward-thinking firing process that ensures the perfect surface consistency to resist stains, limescale, daily wear-and-tear and assist with flush performance.\r\n\r\nTeamed with the BATAFORM® anti-bacterial treatment, the combination ensures an impeccable level of hygiene alongside a luxurious gloss finish, ensuring all round wellbeing in the bathroom.', 700, 620, '11.428571428571429', 'pier-wall-hung-wc-e_w635_h476_1559538066.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:01:06', '2019-06-03 03:01:06'),
(285, 39, NULL, 0, 'Deepstyle 115  high capacity  somestic Rainwater system', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Deepstyle is a semi elliptical system which offers more effective rainwater drainage on larger roof areas. This can&nbsp;reduce&nbsp;the number of downpipes required,&nbsp;providing cost savings and perhaps overall appearance improvements.&nbsp; The system is characterised by an easy fix clip system, which facilitates simple installation whilst external fixing lugs allow easy access for cordless power tools.&nbsp;The Deepstyle system utilises&nbsp;68mm round downpipe and fittings.&nbsp; It is available in six&nbsp;colours including&nbsp;a true&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Anthracite Grey</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">&nbsp;as well as Black, White, Brown,&nbsp;White and Arctic White</span><br></p>', 110, 100, '9.090909090909092', 'Deepstyle 115  high capacity  somestic Rainwater system_1559538074.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:01:14', '2019-06-03 03:01:14'),
(286, 39, NULL, 0, 'Rainwater systems', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Brett Martin’s Rainwater range features a choice of quality PVCu systems in a gloss finish including Roundstyle, Squarestyle, Deepstyle, Prostyle and the high capacity Deepstyle 170 in a variety of colours to suit any building application. Known for its quality, the Brett Martin Rainwater range has been designed to facilitate fast, efficient, economical installation and exceptional reliability which provide the merchant, installer and the end user&nbsp;with satisfaction, peace of mind and a full comprehensive guarantee.</span><br></p>', 120, 100, '16.666666666666664', 'Rainwater systems_1559538175.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:02:55', '2019-06-03 03:02:55'),
(287, 5, NULL, 0, 'Axent One Wall Hung Bidet Toilet Rimless', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">AXENT.ONE is a new generation shower toilet with a series of exceptional functions that can all be controlled using a single knob or via an app. It makes everything superfluous obsolete. Nothing is as hygienic as cleaning with water. It gives us a sense of vitality and vigour. It has the power to heal, restore and rejuvenate. We shower in the morning, bath at night and wash our hands in between. Feeling clean is a part of our lives and is almost as natural as breathing itself. Why then, do we give much less consideration to how we cleanse ourselves after we use the bathroom?</p><p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">AXENT.ONE is fitted with a wash function for a strong but gentle water spray washes you while you are seated on the toilet. The temperature and intensity of the spray can be adjusted easily at the touch of a button. It also comes fully is equipped with a nozzle that is cleaned automatically with fresh water before and after every use, for a more hygienic experience. For water temperature adjustment - simply pull out the multifunction knob, turn it and wait for two ‘beeps’ to sound. The rimless design and stain-resistant surface make the AXENT.ONE easy to clean and the energy saving LED light provides comfortable lighting at night.</p>', 3000, 2995, '0.16666666666666669', 'e80050000019-axentone-shower-toilet-wh_w635_h476_1559538193.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:03:13', '2019-06-03 03:03:13'),
