(289, 39, NULL, 0, 'Rose water systems', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">This&nbsp;social housing&nbsp;project located in Whittlsey, Cambridgeshire includes 16 new modern homes.&nbsp;&nbsp;These days planners in social housing look at all aspects&nbsp;of each building to&nbsp;see where they can save money but not compromise on quality.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">In this particular case&nbsp;the steep roofs required a rainwater system that could cope with a high level of rainwater flow but also&nbsp;provide the necessary&nbsp;quality and cost savings for a modern day social housing project.&nbsp; Brett Martin\'s 115mm Deepstyle White&nbsp;rainwater system offered the solution;&nbsp;facilitating&nbsp;the required capacity flow with all the&nbsp;cost savings&nbsp;of modern day plastics, whilst providing&nbsp;bright&nbsp;and clean&nbsp;looks to&nbsp;finish&nbsp;the homes.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Cost savings can&nbsp;not only be made in specifiying plastic rainwater systems&nbsp;but huge efficiencies&nbsp;can also be made in&nbsp;installation and site costs compared to traditional materials.&nbsp; The fact that the product is lightweight makes it&nbsp;quick and easy to handle, transport and install&nbsp;and working at height is easier and safer.&nbsp; It is corrosion-free, UV stabilised and comes with a quality guarantee.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Brett&nbsp;Martin\'s&nbsp;range of rainwater systems come in a variety of colours including; White (W), Arctic White (A), Black (B), Brown (Br)&nbsp;and Grey (G) and the gutter profile&nbsp;range comprises domestic and high capacity systems.&nbsp;Four styles of domestic gutter (<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/prostyle-106mm-profiled-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/106mm-prostyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">106mm Profiled Ogee</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/roundstyle-112mm-classic-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">112mm Half Round</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/squarestyle-114mm-modern-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/squarestyle-114mm-modern-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">114mm Squarestyle</a>&nbsp;and for larger or steeper roofs, a&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/squarestyle-114mm-modern-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/deepstyle-115mm-high-capacity-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/115mm-deepstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">115mm Deep Profile</a>) utilise 68mm round or 65mm square downpipes. For commercial projects there is a high capacity&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/170mm-deepstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/error.aspx?item=web%3a%7b35814EED-023F-43AC-9C5E-D2F8384D9616%7d%40en-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/error.aspx?item=web%3a%7b35814EED-023F-43AC-9C5E-D2F8384D9616%7d%40en-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\"></a><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/115mm-deepstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">160mm roundstyle</a>&nbsp;gutter with 105mm round and 4” x 3” rectangular downpipe choice</p>', 150, 140, '6.666666666666667', 'Rose Homes 511x220_1559538364.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:06:04', '2019-06-03 03:06:13'),
(290, 5, NULL, 0, 'Axent One PLUS Wall Hung Bidet Toilet Rimless', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">AXENT.ONE is a new generation shower toilet with a series of exceptional functions that can all be controlled using a single knob or via an app. It makes everything superfluous obsolete. Nothing is as hygienic as cleaning with water. It gives us a sense of vitality and vigour. It has the power to heal, restore and rejuvenate. We shower in the morning, bath at night and wash our hands in between. Feeling clean is a part of our lives and is almost as natural as breathing itself. Why then, do we give much less consideration to how we cleanse ourselves after we use the bathroom? WARM AIR DRYER Use the remote control to adjust the temperature of the warm air dryer. The resulting gentle airflow across your skin leaves you feeling clean, fresh and dry.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Axent One PLUS comes complete with a warm air dryer – simply use the remote control to adjust the temperature. The resulting gentle airflow across your skin leaves you feeling clean, fresh and dry. To maximise your comfort as the seasons change, the seat includes adjustable heating that can be set to your individual needs. An integrated sensor detects your presence on the seat and, if set to heat, starts to warm immediately. Once the sensor in the shower toilet seat recognises that you are sitting down the automated deodoriser activates. Utilising the latest diatomite filtration technology, the deodoriser neutralises odours rapidly, enhancing your experience and improving your overall wellbeing. The oscillating shower spray, for rear and feminine wash, provides a thorough, comfortable clean. The gentle spray is pleasant and soothing, and you can easily adjust its position and temperature.</p><div><br></div>', 5000, 4895, '2.1', 'axent-one-rgb-view-side_w635_h476_1559538446.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:07:26', '2019-06-03 03:07:26'),
(291, 39, NULL, 0, 'Artic White Completes Rainwater Colours', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">Brett Martin\'s Rainwater Range includes a both a warm white, simply know as White (W)&nbsp;and&nbsp;bright white, known as Arctic White (A)&nbsp;within the colour options available&nbsp;that also includes Grey (G), Black (B) and Brown (Br).&nbsp; Stocking both white\'s will be an attractive new proposition for merchant stockists as it provides a match to other manufacturer\'s fascia board colour variations all from one supplier.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">A range of profiles are also available in all colours including&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/prostyle-106mm-profiled-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">106mm Prostyle</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/roundstyle-112mm-classic-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">112mm Roundstyle</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/squarestyle-114mm-modern-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">114mm Squarestyle</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/deepstyle-115mm-high-capacity-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">115mm Deepstyle</a>&nbsp;that all have corresponding fixtures and fittings.&nbsp;&nbsp;A high capacity&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/error.aspx?item=web%3a%7b35814EED-023F-43AC-9C5E-D2F8384D9616%7d%40en-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">160mm Industrial system</a>&nbsp;for large agricultural and commercial applications with high flow capacities is also available in Grey (G), Black (B) and Brown (Br).</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">Demand for colour variations and profile options&nbsp;in rainwater systems has grown due to the number of Specifiers, Contractors and Developers specifying bespoke&nbsp;rainwater systems&nbsp;to match the unique styles&nbsp;of new and renovated homes and housing developments that are designed to stand out from the crowd and create the necessary \'wow factor\' which is so important in the housing market.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">Brett Martin Plumbing and Drainage Sales Director Graham Smith suggests “The housing market these days is very sensitive and developers and contractors must have an eye for detail in order to create that all important quality exterior finish.&nbsp; Something as simple as matching rainwater systems with fascia boards can make the difference between achieving the first appearances wow factor&nbsp;to potential buyers”.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">Graham Continues “With the full colour range now available available in a range of profiles Specifiers and Contractors&nbsp;will be able to achieve an excellent match to other manufacturer\'s fascia board colour variations all from one supplier”.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; line-height: 16.8px; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;\">To enquire about stocking Brett Martin Arctic White or any other Rainwater System colours and profiles&nbsp;please call&nbsp;<strong>01246 280000&nbsp;</strong>or email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:building@brettmartin.com\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">building@brettmartin.com</a>.&nbsp; Ireland Customers please call&nbsp;<strong>028&nbsp;</strong>(ROI-<strong>048</strong>)<strong>&nbsp;9084 8999</strong>&nbsp;or email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sales@brettmartin.com\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">sales@brettmartin.com</a></p>', 110, 100, '9.090909090909092', 'Artic White Completes Rainwater Colours_1559538529.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:08:49', '2019-06-03 03:08:49'),
(292, 39, NULL, 0, 'Green olive Cascade Feaured on 19th century truckers Hatch', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\">Green Olive&nbsp;Cascade Cast Iron Style Rainwater Systems were used on the renovation of a 19<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;Century property in West Sussex.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\">Built in 1883, as part of the Hyde estate, the house originally featured traditional cast iron ogee style guttering, painted green to tie in with the property’s fascia and soffits.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\">Cascade was chosen due to its range of six heritage colour options, reflecting the trend for priming and painting traditional systems and both 106mm Prostyle and 112mm Roundstyle Guttering, along with 68mm round downpipe, were installed, replacing the existing cast iron.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-size: 8pt;\">In this particular installation, Cascade provided a cost effective alternative to cast iron, offering the benefits of modern plastic materials while still maintaining the traditional aesthetic of the period style home.</span></p>', 150, 140, '6.666666666666667', 'Green olive Cascade Feaured on 19th century truckers Hatch_1559538634.JPG', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:10:34', '2019-06-03 03:10:34');
