(293, 39, NULL, 0, 'lagan view', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">A new development of detached and semi-detached properties in Donaghcloney has benefitted from the elegant lines of Brett Martin\'s Rainwater System. The development uses 106mm Prostyle gutter with a combination of 65mm square downpipe and&nbsp;68mm round downpipe. The 110mm Push-fit soil system in black has been installed to complete the look.</p><div><br></div>', 120, 115, '4.166666666666666', 'laganview_1559538757.jpg', '1', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:12:37', '2019-06-03 03:12:37'),
(294, 39, NULL, 0, 'Anthracite Grey Rainwater Range', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Brett Martin Plumbing and Drainage is now offering the popular Anthracite Grey colour option within both the standard Rainwater range and the Cascade Cast Iron Style Rainwater and Soil System range, allowing merchants and their customers to capitalise on the growing market trend for this colour on windows and doors on both new build and renovation projects.&nbsp;<br><br>Specifically developed to create an exact colour match to the true RAL 7016 Anthracite Grey, Brett Martin’s new colour option is the best Anthracite Grey colour tone on the market and perfectly complements other building accessories.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\">From the standard Rainwater range, the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-prostyle-106-profiled-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Prostyle 106mm&nbsp;</a>gutter profile is designed with sleek lines due to its classic ‘ogee’ profile, giving it a modern appearance, making it ideal for both refurbishment and new build contemporary properties. This profile is used with the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/prostyle-106mm-profiled-domestic-system/65mm-square-downpipe.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">65mm Square Downpipe</a>.&nbsp;The&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-deepstyle-115-high-capacity-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Deepstyle 115mm</a>&nbsp;gutter profile and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-deepstyle-115-high-capacity-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">68mm Downpipe</a>&nbsp;System is designed to offer effective rainwater drainage on large roofs of domestic and commercial buildings. Manufactured in weatherable uPVC, and complete with a 10 year warranty, the rich gloss appearance of the new Anthracite Grey option will last for years to come. Deepstyle 115 is also available in a choice of Black, Grey, Brown, White and Arctic White colour options.&nbsp;<br><br>“Our Anthracite Grey offers the perfect colour match to RAL 7016 and will give specifiers the opportunity to have the exact match, ensuring rainwater and soil systems are in line with the overall building aesthetic, whether they are windows, doors or other roofing components,” said Hayley Lowry, Marketing Manager of Brett Martin.&nbsp;<br><br>Responding to the popularity of the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-cascade-cast-iron-style-rainwater-and-soil-systems.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Cascade Cast Iron Style Rainwater&nbsp;</a>and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-soil-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Soil System&nbsp;</a>the new Anthracite Grey colour option is also available across all Cascade gutter profiles, downpipes, fittings and accessory items. Designed with full consideration to original features, dimensions and detailing, the high quality Cascade pipework, fittings and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-hoppers.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">hoppers</a>&nbsp;create a cast iron look for less. In addition to Anthracite Grey, the Cascade range is available in Classic Black, Oxford Blue, Olive Green, Graphite Grey, Sandstone and Porcelain White.&nbsp;<br><br>The addition of the new Anthracite Grey colour option to an already comprehensive range of domestic and industrial gutter and pipework profiles, allows merchants to offer their customers more products and with the knowledge that these Rainwater systems are fully compatible with both existing cast iron and modern-style rainwater systems, meaning there’s increased potential for merchants to increase sales</p>', 150, 140, '6.666666666666667', 'Anthracite_Grey_Rainwater_Systems_1559538855.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:14:15', '2019-06-03 03:14:15'),
(295, 37, NULL, 0, 'Belgravia 450mm showerhead', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">An exceptional range designed for those with a taste for tradition, Belgravia combines quality craftsmanship with a hand-polished finish to bring you the finest selection of basin and bath taps. Beautiful detailing seen in the ceramic handles and inscribed Belgravia indices set this collection apart, creating a bathroom that is period in style yet superior in function.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Introducing a touch of hotel-inspired luxury to bathrooms, the beautiful chrome surface of our traditional Belgravia brassware range is meticulously hand polished for a reflective, high-shine exterior. Also offered in a lustrous nickel finish, perfect for adding an element of glamour to your bath.&nbsp;</p>', 1095, 1059, '3.287671232876712', 'FH18C_pl (1)_1559538931.jpg', '1', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:15:31', '2019-06-03 03:15:31'),
(296, 5, NULL, 0, 'Axent One PLUS Back to Wall Bidet Toilet Rimless', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">AXENT.ONE is a new generation shower toilet with a series of exceptional functions that can all be controlled using a single knob or via an app. It makes everything superfluous obsolete. Nothing is as hygienic as cleaning with water. It gives us a sense of vitality and vigour. It has the power to heal, restore and rejuvenate. We shower in the morning, bath at night and wash our hands in between. Feeling clean is a part of our lives and is almost as natural as breathing itself. Why then, do we give much less consideration to how we cleanse ourselves after we use the bathroom? WARM AIR DRYER Use the remote control to adjust the temperature of the warm air dryer. The resulting gentle airflow across your skin leaves you feeling clean, fresh and dry.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Axent One PLUS comes complete with a warm air dryer – simply use the remote control to adjust the temperature. The resulting gentle airflow across your skin leaves you feeling clean, fresh and dry. To maximise your comfort as the seasons change, the seat includes adjustable heating that can be set to your individual needs. An integrated sensor detects your presence on the seat and, if set to heat, starts to warm immediately. Once the sensor in the shower toilet seat recognises that you are sitting down the automated deodoriser activates. Utilising the latest diatomite filtration technology, the deodoriser neutralises odours rapidly, enhancing your experience and improving your overall wellbeing. The oscillating shower spray, for rear and feminine wash, provides a thorough, comfortable clean. The gentle spray is pleasant and soothing, and you can easily adjust its position and temperature.</p><div><br></div>', 5200, 5100, '1.9230769230769231', 'axent-one-plus-rgb-btw-remote_w635_h476_1559538981.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:16:21', '2019-06-03 03:16:21'),
(297, 39, NULL, 0, 'Anthracite Grey special edition', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Anthracite Grey is the latest colour option to be added to the Brett Martin Rainwater range. Responding to the trend for windows and doors in this popular colour, in both new build and refurbishment projects, Anthracite Grey gutters and downpipes allow homeowners and builders to fully complement the building’s accessories. Perfectly colour matched to RAL 7016 Brett Martin’s Anthracite Grey is a true colour match compared to other systems on the market. The range includes the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-prostyle-106-profiled-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Prostyle</a><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">&nbsp;106mm Gutter and 65mm Square Downpipe&nbsp;System;&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-roundstyle-112-half-round-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Roundstyle</a><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">112mm Gutter and 68mm Round Downpipe;&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-deepstyle-115-high-capacity-domestic-rainwater-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Deepstyle</a><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">&nbsp;115mm and&nbsp;68mm Round Downpipe - all&nbsp;in a modern gloss finish&nbsp;and all products in the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey/anthracite-grey-cascade-cast-iron-style-rainwater-and-soil-systems.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Cascade</a><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">&nbsp;Cast Iron Style range.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', 150, 150, '0', 'Anthracite_Grey_Rainwater_Systems (1)_1559539025.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:17:06', '2019-06-03 03:17:06'),
(298, 5, NULL, 0, 'Pier Wall Hung RIMLESS Toilet & Soft Close Seat', NULL, 'Small bathrooms no longer have to compromise when it comes to great design and first-class function. The Pier Toilet, a contemporary yet very simple toilet, has the shortest projection on the market at a minimal 43cm.\r\n\r\nNot only compact, the seat is still extremely comfortable and fits perfectly in limited spaces, whilst the high-function flush performance is as good as it gets.Introducing an innovation in ceramic glaze technology, Pier is expertly crafted from CERASLIDE®; a forward-thinking firing process that ensures the perfect surface consistency to resist stains, limescale, daily wear-and-tear and assist with flush performance.\r\n\r\nTeamed with the BATAFORM® anti-bacterial treatment, the combination ensures an impeccable level of hygiene alongside a luxurious gloss finish, ensuring all round wellbeing in the bathroom.', 700, 655, '6.428571428571428', 'pier-wall-hung-wc-d_w635_h476_1559539075.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:17:55', '2019-06-03 03:17:55'),
(299, 5, NULL, 0, 'Glide II Gloss White Wall Hung Short Projection Rimless Toilet & Soft Close Seat', NULL, NULL, 600, 529, '11.833333333333334', 'gl6115cw-gl6106w-side_w635_h476_1559539133.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:18:53', '2019-06-03 03:19:55'),
(300, 39, NULL, 0, 'Killyleagh Georgian Home systems', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">This&nbsp;refurbishment of a Georgian styled cottage in the village of Killyleagh in Northern Ireland included the installation of a new Rainwater System. In this particular case, the home owner specified a gutter and downpipe system to match the anthracite grey fascia and also cope with large amounts of rainwater as some of the roof areas were steep whilst also keeping within a tight budget.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Perfectly colour matched to RAL 7016 the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/deepstyle-115mm-high-capacity-domestic-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Deepstyle 115mm</a>&nbsp;gutter system and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/deepstyle-115mm-high-capacity-domestic-system/68mm-round-downpipe.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">68mm Round Downpipe</a>, both in Anthracite Grey, were the perfect solution;&nbsp;assisting&nbsp;the required capacity flow with all the&nbsp;cost savings&nbsp;of modern day plastics, whilst providing&nbsp;a consistent colour scheme across a range of&nbsp;building accessories.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Find out more about&nbsp;the complete&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/rainwater-systems/anthracite-grey.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Anthracite Grey&nbsp;</a>Rainwater Systems available from Brett Martin.</p>', 115, 110, '4.3478260869565215', 'Killyleagh Georgian Home systems_1559539137.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:18:57', '2019-06-03 03:18:57'),
(301, 39, NULL, 0, 'Bournemouth Post War Home systems', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma;\">The Cascade Cast Iron Style Rainwater System was used on the renovation of this post war property in Bournemouth.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma;\">The authentic cast iron style system&nbsp;was specified by Scott Worsfold Architects as a cost effective and easy to fit rainwater solution and in keeping with the style of architecture. To complement the ‘arts and crafts’ aesthetics of the property the Cascade&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/112mm-roundstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">112mm Roundstyle Gutter&nbsp;</a>and 68mm Round Downpipe systems plus 2 x Gothic design&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-hoppers.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">hoppers</a>, all in Classic Black were installed.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma;\">To read the full case study on this project,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/news-events/cascade-case-study-gary-worsfold.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">click here</a>&nbsp;or find out more on the complete range of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Cascade</a>Cast Iron Style Rainwater range.</span></p>', 150, 140, '6.666666666666667', 'Bournemouth Post War Home systems_1559539237.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:20:37', '2019-06-03 03:20:37'),
(302, 39, NULL, 0, 'Berewood Village Waterlooville systems', NULL, '<div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">A new housing development at Waterlooville in Hampshire has reached the halfway point in the construction of 193 new homes that form the first phase of the Berewood Village scheme. For their traditional-style aesthetic, Cascade\'s&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/115mm-deepstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">115mm Deepstyle</a>&nbsp;rainwater system and 68mm round downpipe was specified to combine a heritage aesthetic, simple installation and a low maintenance solution.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Built on a 168-acre plot next to the town of Waterlooville, the 2, 3 and 4 bedroom homes signal the start of a brand new ‘garden city’ that will comprise 2,500 homes, two schools, offices, retail, and two new pubs. Following years of careful planning and community consultation, the first part of the scheme is being built by Bloor Homes with a high standard of specification.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">In line with the garden city concept of well-designed homes, green spaces and community facilities, every private dwelling is being delivered with incredible attention to detail. Cascade fitted the bill perfectly as the rainwater system that complemented the traditional design, met with planning approval and delivered long term performance.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Manufactured with modern plastic materials,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Cascade</a>&nbsp;offers a traditional appearance without the cast-iron price tag. &nbsp;Costing a fraction of the price to buy, install and maintain, Cascade can replace an aluminium or cast iron rainwater specification to deliver projects under budget, ahead of schedule and exceeding expectations.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Also available in&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/106mm-prostyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">106mm Prostyle</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/112mm-roundstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">112mm Roundstyle</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/170mm-deepstyle.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">160mm High Capacity</a>&nbsp;rainwater systems and a complementary&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-soil-system.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">110mm Push-Fit Soil system</a>, Cascade offers several gutter profiles and downpipe styles which are suitable for new build and renovation projects. &nbsp;And to retain the authentic style, each element of the system has been carefully designed to replicate original features, dimensions and detailing. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">Brett Martin’s extensive range of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-hoppers.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">hoppers</a>&nbsp;– including traditional Ogee, Bath and Gothic styles – allows the designer and homeowner to individualise their rainwater system, whilst a choice of period motifs includes Tudor Rose, Fleur de Lys, Lion and Gargoyles. In addition to Classic Black, the system can be supplied in a&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.brettmartin.com/en-gb/plumbing-and-drainage/products/cast-iron/cast-iron-style-colours.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(93, 120, 107); text-decoration-line: underline;\">choice of heritage colours</a>&nbsp;including Oxford Blue, Olive Green, Graphite Grey, Sandstone and Porcelain White. Fully UV stabilised, the Cascade systems are protected with a 10 year colour warranty.&nbsp;</div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11.2px;\">With the first phase of the stunning Berewood Village scheme at the halfway point, Brett Martin’s Cascade range of cast iron style gutter and downpipe profiles is once again set to provide a stylish and classic aesthetic at a new-build housing development that will not only meet the needs of the architect and developer, but the new residents too.</div>', 120, 120, '0', 'Berewood Village Waterlooville systems_1559539333.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:22:13', '2019-06-03 03:22:13'),
