(314, 42, NULL, 0, 'Sanitary Macerator Waste Pump System for Toilet, Basin + Bath ME90103', NULL, '<p><span class=\"tabContentTitle\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); display: block; font-family: arial;\">Description</span></p><div id=\"divProdLongDesc\" class=\"prodDesc\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 12px; float: left; line-height: 20px; width: 660px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: verdana;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">Macerator Sanitary Waste Pump System Sewage Pumping 3 Inlets ME90103</strong><br><br>This systems allows to transport sewage from the most remote areas in your house. Possible to connect 1 toilet and unlimited other sanitary devices (bath, shower, sink, ...) on one entry. Also suitable for dishwashers and washing machines. Includes all accessories to connect a toilet and multiple other sanitary devices. Plastic covers are included to close the entries that are unused. Up to 70m horizontal discharge, 7m vertical discharge. The shower outlet must be a minimum of 210mm above floor level.</span></div>', 170, 170, '0', 'Sanitary Macerator Waste Pump System for Toilet, Basin + Bath ME90103_1559540037.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:33:57', '2019-06-03 03:33:57'),
(315, 41, NULL, 0, 'Sanitary Macerator Waste Pump System for Toilet, Basin + Bath ME90101', NULL, '<p><span class=\"tabContentTitle\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); display: block; font-family: arial;\">Description</span></p><div id=\"divProdLongDesc\" class=\"prodDesc\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 12px; float: left; line-height: 20px; width: 660px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: verdana;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">Macerator Sanitary Waste Pump System Sewage Pumping 4 Inlets Inc. Integrated Carbon Filter (no odors!) ME90101</strong><br><br>This systems allows to transport sewage from the most remote areas in your house. Possible to connect 1 toilet and unlimited other sanitary devices (bath, shower, sink, ...) on one entry. Also suitable for dishwashers and washing machines. Includes all accessories to connect a toilet and multiple other sanitary devices. Plastic covers are included to close the entries that are unused. Up to 80m horizontal discharge, 8m vertical discharge. Powerful motor with integrated stainless steel shredder, more powerful compared to the 600W model and offers lower power consumption. Entry available at the LEFT AND RIGHT side of the macerator.</span></div>', 220, 220, '0', 'Sanitary Macerator Waste Pump System for Toilet, Basin + Bath ME90101_1559540118.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:35:19', '2019-06-03 03:35:19'),
