(317, 41, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Sanicom 1 - Grey Waste Water Pump', NULL, '<div class=\"info-tabs__tab\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 20px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 56, 70); background: rgb(246, 249, 250); transition: border 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 56, 70); font-family: &quot;Novecento Wide&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1em; display: inline; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s;\">Description</h3></div><div class=\"info-tabs__content\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(246, 249, 250); width: 766.938px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><div class=\"info-tabs__content__wrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 145.375px 0px 0px; width: 872.313px; overflow: hidden scroll; scroll-behavior: smooth; max-height: 700px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">With the Saniflo Sanicom Heavy Duty Pump, nursing homes, laundries, and similar high volume facilities can be assured of efficient pumping of their waste. Made of grey polyethylene, this pump measures 330mm high, 490mm wide, and 230mm in diameter. There are two side entries measuring 40mm. The discharge pipework measures 32mm and 40mm. With a maximum vertical discharge height of 9mm, this heavy duty pump has a motor that is made of aluminium and has a stainless steel shaft. The motor is power rated at 695 watts. The working temperature of this pump is 65 degrees Celsius with a maximum temperature of 90 degrees Celsius for ten minutes. The thermal bulb of this pump has a bimetallicstrip. This unit includes a pressure switch and a pressure chamber tube.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Colour: Acrylic</p></div></div>', 834, 800, '4.07673860911271', 'Saniflo Sanicom 1 - Grey Waste Water Pump_1559540290.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:38:10', '2019-06-03 03:38:10'),
(318, 41, NULL, 0, 'Stuart Turner Wasteflo WC3 Cloakroom Macerator', NULL, '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">With the Stuart Turner Wasteflo WC3 Cloakroom Macerator, almost any area can easily be transformed into an en-suite or bathroom. The sleek and slim design features an inlet that measures 32mm and an outlet that measures 32mm. With a maximum liquid temperature of 50 degrees Celius, a minimum liquid temperature of 4 degrees Celicius, and a maximum ambient temperature of 40 degrees Celcius, this macerator allows adaptations for a wide range of situations. The removable cassette system enables all the mechanical and electrical systems to be housed in one area making cleaning an easy and simple task. Because this macerator is quiet and emits less than 60 dBs, it can be housed anywhere necessary. Its ability to pump horizontally up to 52 m or vertically up to 5 m assures powerful performance in this compact design.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">Colour: White</p>', 397, 397, '0', 'Stuart Turner Wasteflo WC3 Cloakroom Macerator_1559540436.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:40:36', '2019-06-03 03:40:36'),
(319, 41, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Up - The Original Saniflo Macerator', NULL, '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">Add a water closet in your basement, and you increase the value of your home. You add convenience. You face a potential plumbing nightmare. Plumbing vents up, toward your roof, and that\'s why you need something to force water upward if you place it too low. In other words, you need the original Saniflo macerator to make your plumbing work. This handy little machine takes water closet waste and delivers it where it needs to go. It works perfectly with vertical plumbing systems. Inside, the Saniflo macerator is made with an induction motor, no brushes or gears that will wear out in time. The wide casing design reduces noise. The original Saniflo macerator is made with hard-wearing neoprene, stainless steel, polypropylene and C.R.P., and it\'s made to last.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">Please note: The dimensions shown here are of the unit only and do not allow for these additional space requirements as they may differ for each installation. It is the responsibility of the purchaser or installer to ensure that the Saniflo product selected will fit in the chosen place of installation with due allowance for pipework runs, electrical connections etc.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">For best installation practice please observe the following:</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">Avoid any contact with the walls of the room when fitting the tank.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Make sure that the anti-vibration pads are properly stuck underneath the tank at the</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">indicated locations, to minimize vibrations.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Screw the fastening tabs to the floor to prevent the appliance from moving.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Position the tank on a perfectly level floor so that the anti-vibration pads can work effectively.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Fasten the outlet piping correctly avoiding any distances between attachments in</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">excess of one metre.</p>', 373, 373, '0', 'Saniflo Up - The Original Saniflo Macerator_1559540503.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:41:43', '2019-06-03 03:41:43'),
(320, 37, NULL, 0, 'Belgravia Crosshead Single Outlet Thermostatic Shower Valve', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">An exceptional range designed for those with a taste for tradition, Belgravia combines quality craftsmanship with a hand-polished finish to bring you the finest selection of basin and bath taps. Beautiful detailing seen in the ceramic handles and inscribed Belgravia indices set this collection apart, creating a bathroom that is period in style yet superior in function.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Introducing a touch of hotel-inspired luxury to bathrooms, the beautiful chrome surface of our traditional Belgravia brassware range is meticulously hand polished for a reflective, high-shine exterior. Also offered in a lustrous nickel finish, perfect for adding an element of glamour to your bath.&nbsp;</p>', 675, 649, '3.851851851851852', 'HG1000RN_pl_1559540545.jpg', '1', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:42:25', '2019-06-03 03:42:25'),
(321, 43, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Domestic - SANICOMPACT - SANI14', NULL, '<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">Saniflo Domestic - SANICOMPACT - SANI14</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">The Sanicompact is a unique macerator, It is a concealed macerator built into a cisternless toilet with flush button installed on pan. Sanicompact is part of the domestic range from the industry leading manufacturer Saniflo.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">When the toilet is flushed or basin drained the Sanitop macerator activates to pump waste horizontally to a remote soil pipe up to 30 metres away. Sanitop can also be configured to pump waste vertically up to 3 metres if required.</span><br></p>', 700, 700, '0', 'Saniflo Domestic - SANICOMPACT - SANI14_1559540570.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:42:50', '2019-06-03 03:42:50'),
(322, 43, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Domestic - SANISHOWER - SANI08', NULL, '<p><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">The Sanishower is a macerator to be used for a shower and basin where gravity drainage will be different ie- basement or internal wall. Sanishower is part of the domestic range from the industry leading manufacturer Saniflo.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">When the basin or shower is drained the Sanishower macerator activates to pump waste horizontally to a remote soil pipe up to 40 metres away. Sanitop can also be configured to pump waste vertically up to 4 metres if required.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Dimensions - W296mm x H145mm x D165mm</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">For use with - Shower and Wash Basin</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pumps Vertically - 4 M</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pumps Horizontally - 40 M&nbsp;</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Discharge Pipe - 22mm</li></ul>', 370, 369, '0.2702702702702703', 'Saniflo Domestic - SANISHOWER - SANI08_1559540628.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 03:43:48', '2019-06-03 03:43:48'),
