(333, 42, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Domestic - SANIPACK - SANI09 commercial', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">The Sanipack is a macerator designed to fit completely concealed within furniture or wall spaces. Sanipack is part of the domestic range from the industry leading manufacturer Saniflo. The unit is extra slim to make concealment easy and can be used for toilet, basin and shower.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">When the toilet is flushed or outlets drained the Sanipack macerator activates to pump waste horizontally to a remote soil pipe up to 40 metres away. Sanitop can also be configured to pump waste vertically up to 4 metres if required.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"></p><ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Dimensions - W426mm x H362mm x D120mm</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">For use with - Toilet/WC and Wash Basin</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pumps Vertically - 4 M</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pumps Horizontally - 40 M&nbsp;</li><li style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Discharge Pipe - 22mm</li></ul>', 575, 540, '6.086956521