(334, 42, NULL, 0, 'Saniflo Saniwall Macerator with WC Frame', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 104, 108); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(246, 249, 250);\">With a dual flush cistern, wall hung toilet frame, and wall plate, the Saniflo-Saniwall 6110 Macerator combines all the functions needed for an efficient toilet. This system is concealed in a wall to save space in a bathroom, and it is suitable for use with most standard toilets, including wall-hung models. It has a standard fixing distance of 18-23cm and comes with installation instructions that are easy to read. Additionally, the dual flush uses only 3-6 litres of water to conserve as much as possible while still allowing the macerator to function properly. Included with this Saniflo-Saniwall macerator is a stopcock, float valve, and standard chrome control plate. The dimensions are 630 x 1075 x 194 with a discharge pipe diameter of 22/32mm and the motor runs on 400 watts of power with 2,800 rpm. Installing this macerator helps the user conserve water without sacrificing convenience.</span><br></p>', 717, 714, '0.41841004184100417', 'Saniflo Saniwall Macerator with WC Frame_1559541692.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:01:32', '2019-06-03 04:01:32'),
