(359, 44, NULL, 0, 'Ideal Standard Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Heavy Duty Kitchen Sink', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The unique large design of the Belfast ceramic single bowl sink from Ideal Standard is the perfect choice for commercial applications. The generously sized single bowl measures an impressive 460&nbsp;x 380&nbsp;x 210mm giving you plenty of room to work with.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Belfast sink is made from heavy duty fireclay. Fireclay is an extremely hard-wearing material, making it perfect for use in a busy kitchen as it is&nbsp;resistant to scratches, chipping and even heat- so you can place a hot pan down without worry of any damage. It is also resistant to acids, alkalis and staining meaning it maintains its pristine appearance and surface finish for a product life-time.</span></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/belfast-sinks-420-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">Belfast sinks</a>&nbsp;have been a popular style of sink dating far back to the 1700’s due to the robust build and attractive design. The deep bowl guarantees durability and practicality, allowing of plenty of room for washing all of your pots and pans. The sink is also reversible to allow for any positioning in the kitchen.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The sink comes with a weir overflow which helps to prevent overspill, allowing water to drain away without the risk of flooding.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Ideal Standard Belfast Sink conforms to BS 1206:1974 and has a lifetime guarantee so you have important peace of mind.</span></p>', 145, 140, '3.4482758620689653', 'Ideal Standard Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Heavy Duty Kitchen Sink_1559542641.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:17:21', '2019-06-03 04:17:21'),
