(361, 44, NULL, 0, 'Twyfords Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Kitchen Sink', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The traditional Belfast sink by Twyford is a popular choice for any kitchen with its minimalist design and extremely practical large deep singe bowl with an impressive measurement of 255 x 560 x 425mm.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Belfast sink is made from heavy duty fireclay. Fireclay is an extremely hard-wearing material, making it perfect for use in a kitchen as it has a stain resistant surface that is easy to clean and keep looking new for longer. This sink can also be hung from the wall by using built-in brackets for masonry walls and screw to wall brackets for timber frame walls.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The practical deep single bowl gives you plenty of room for washing all of your pots and pans.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/belfast-sinks-420-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">Belfast sinks</a>&nbsp;have been a popular style of sink dating far back to the 1700’s due to the robust build and attractive design.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Twyford Belfast Sink comes with a 1 year guarantee for added peace of mind.</span></p>', 200, 199, '0.5', 'Twyfords Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Kitchen Sink_1559542698.png', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:18:18', '2019-06-03 04:18:18'),
