(364, 44, NULL, 0, 'RAK Ceramics Gourmet Kitchen Sink 8 Belfast Style with Weir Overflow', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you want to freshen up your kitchen, look no further than RAK Ceramic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/kitchen-sinks-78-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">kitchen sinks</a>. This global brand produces premium kitchen items that are sold in over 150 countries around the world. The crisp lines and clean design of their products sets them a cut above competitors, and they are the first company from UEA to hold the ISO 9001 certification for quality ceramics.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">As with all of RAK’s ceramic products, the Gourmet Belfast Style Sink is a gorgeous piece of workmanship that has undergone thorough quality control checks to ensure it is as accessible and long-lasting as it is beautiful.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">For those seeking a more rustic, country house-style sink, the Belfast style model is an excellent choice. The sink is fitted into an existing mount and can either be incorporated into it or sit as a freestanding sink on top.</span></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 2.45rem;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Features &amp; Benefits</span></span></span></h3><ul style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Charming traditional Belfast Style sink for the rustic European kitchen</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Finished with a durable gloss in crisp white - perfect for use in the kitchen and easy to keep clean</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Fully reversible orientation - it can easily be fitted into your desired space</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Clean, simple design makes it straightforward to install and maintain</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Traditional plug waste disposal</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Suitable for use with a 1 bowl plumbing kit</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quality guaranteed - comes with a 10-year warranty</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">This gorgeous sink is perfect for customers seeking a vintage-inspired look to their kitchen. The RAK Ceramics Gourmet Sink 8 Belfast Style sink combines the eternally charming Belfast style with contemporary design: the result is a flawless yet unpretentious kitchen sink.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">At Plumbworld, we are proud stockists of a RAK’s broad range of kitchen and bathroom ceramics. For more information on the RAK Sink 8 Belfast Style sink, or to have a chat about your plans for your new kitchen, get in touch with us and one of our team will be able to help.</span></p>', 165, 162, '1.8181818181818181', 'RAK Ceramics Gourmet Kitchen Sink 8 Belfast Style with Weir Overflow_1559542823.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:20:23', '2019-06-03 04:20:23'),
