(381, 46, NULL, 0, 'Reginox Tuscany Undermount White Ceramic 1.5 Bowl Kitchen Sink with Waste Included', NULL, '<ul style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><li>Stunning ceramic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/kitchen-sinks-78-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">kitchen sink</a>&nbsp;combines elements of traditional and contemporary aesthetic</li><li>Undermount installation style represents cutting edge of kitchen design</li><li>1.5 bowls offer plenty of space for washing, rinsing and draining</li><li>Reversible for left- or right-hand orientation as per your preference</li><li>Resistant to staining and heat damage</li><li>10-year guarantee from Reginox with each purchase</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">In days gone by, ceramic sinks have been more commonplace in traditional kitchens. However, a resurgence in their popularity of late has seen them become a familiar fixture in modern and contemporary spaces, as well. The undermount installation style of this stunning Tuscany 1.5 bowl sink from Reginox adds to that aesthetic, taking advantage of one of the hottest trends in kitchen design to catapult the ceramic sink into the 21<span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">st</span>&nbsp;century. With a gleaming white finish and attractively curved edges, the Tuscany undermount is sure to complement the existing décor of any home it inhabits.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">There’s plenty more to this product’s charms than just surface ones, however. With a 1.5 bowl capacity, both of which boast generous proportions (400mm x 388mm x 174mm for the main bowl and 100mm x 286mm x 150mm for the secondary bowl), there’s plenty of room to wash, soak, rinse and drain all the crockery in your cupboards if need be. What’s more, the super-tough ceramic from which the sinks are constructed is resistant to temperature and staining, meaning you can place hot pots and pans directly onto their surface without fear of burning or marking them. The hygienic design also makes cleaning up a cakewalk; simply wipe with a damp cloth and they’ll instantly return to their impeccable former brilliance.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">All purchases come with twin waste plugs and strainers for both of the sinks, as well as a 10-year guarantee from the manufacturer, which covers all parts for a single year. With that kind of peace of mind on offer, can you afford not to invest in a Reginox Tuscany undermount sink? The future of contemporary kitchen design awaits.</p>', 166, 166, '0', 'Reginox Tuscany Undermount White Ceramic 1.5 Bowl Kitchen Sink with Waste Included_1559544357.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:45:57', '2019-06-03 04:45:57'),
(382, 46, NULL, 0, 'Reginox Mataro Undermount White Ceramic Single Bowl Kitchen Sink with Waste Included', NULL, '<ul style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><li>White ceramic single bowl&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/kitchen-sinks-78-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">kitchen sink</a>&nbsp;is perfect marriage of simplicity and sophistication</li><li>Undermount installation creates cool aesthetic and aids clean-up</li><li>Sink dimensions are large enough to handle the whole family’s washing up</li><li>Waste plug and strainer included as standard</li><li>Each unit comes with 10-year manufacturer’s warranty</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Are you looking for a new kitchen sink which combines performance, panache and a reasonable price in one neat package? Look no further. The Reginox Mataro single bowl sink is at the cutting edge of home design trends, with its undermount installation technique making the sink a feature in itself. Made from fireclay ceramic and with a cool white finish, the basin is guaranteed to give your existing décor a boost and bring it soaring into the 21<span style=\"position: relative; font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">st</span>century.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">It’s far from just a pretty face, however. The undermount installation of the sink looks fantastic, but also serves an important function when it comes to maintenance; with nowhere for food crumbs and other waste to hide, cleaning up becomes a matter of mere child’s play. The basin itself is made from durable materials that are both heat- and stain-resistant, while the ultra-smooth surface of the sink won’t fade or become discoloured over time. And with dimensions of 440mm x 545mm x 178mm, the generous proportions are big enough to easily handle the whole family’s crockery and cutlery, but the lack of a separate drainer means it doesn’t take up as much room in the kitchen as some other models.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">All units are supplied with a waste plug and strainer as standard and a 10-year manufacturer’s warranty, with a one-year guarantee on all parts. As such, it’s a hugely attractive and handsomely affordable sink which will serve you and your family well for many years to come.</p>', 145, 144, '0.6896551724137931', 'Reginox Mataro Undermount White Ceramic Single Bowl Kitchen Sink with Waste Included_1559544408.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:46:48', '2019-06-03 04:46:48'),
