(384, 46, NULL, 0, 'Reginox Traditional Black Ceramic 1.0 Kitchen Sink + Brooklyn Mixer Tap', NULL, '<p><span class=\"tabContentTitle\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); display: block; font-family: arial;\">Description</span></p><div id=\"divProdLongDesc\" class=\"prodDesc\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 12px; float: left; line-height: 20px; width: 660px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: verdana;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">Reginox Traditional Black Ceramic 1.0 Kitchen Sink + Brooklyn Mixer Tap<br><br></strong>Victorian plumbing brings together 2 excellent products from the industry leading kitchen brand Reginox.<br><br>The traditional black ceramic sink feats 1.0 bowl, although classic in design, Reginox use the latest design and manufacturing methods to achieve amazing results. The Brooklyn tap is included in this pack, the tap is a traditional chrome mixer with dual lever function. The combination of these 2 products together create a beautiful traditional centrepiece for any kitchen.</span></div>', 310, 300, '3.225806451612903', 'Reginox Traditional Black Ceramic 1.0 Kitchen Sink + Brooklyn Mixer Tap_1559544594.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:49:54', '2019-06-03 04:49:54'),
(385, 46, NULL, 0, 'Miller - New York 120 Wall Hung Four Drawer Vanity Unit with Double Ceramic Basin - Black', NULL, '<p><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">The smoothly styled New York collection features sharp and minimalist elegance. This black stained oak finish&nbsp;120 Wall Hung Four Drawer Vanity Unit with Double Ceramic Basin features soft closing drawers, the drawers are sturdy, fully extendable and fitted with anti-slip mats. The top drawers have compartments in white painted wood that can easily be lifted out for cleaning and the bottom drawers are fitted with an adjustable bar to stop larger items from moving. This unit also comprises of a D-shaped bowl double ceramic basin with a tap hole for each bowl and a set of four stylish chrome handles. Fitted with mounting rails and brackets for adjustable and quick installation.</span><br></p>', 1600, 1599, '0.0625', 'Miller - New York 120 Wall Hung Four Drawer Vanity Unit with Double Ceramic Basin - Black_1559544650.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:50:50', '2019-06-03 04:50:50'),
(386, 46, NULL, 0, 'Reginox Contemporary White Ceramic 1.0 Bowl Kitchen Sink RL504CW + Tap', NULL, '<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold;\">Reginox Contemporary White Ceramic 1.0 Bowl Kitchen Sink RL504CW + Modern Chrome Tap</strong><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">This Reginox Contemporary White Ceramic 1.0 Bowl Kitchen Sink with modern chrome tap is from the Regi-Ceramic range, made from the highest grade fine fireclay it is able to withstand the daily uses of the kitchen. This inset sink requires a minimum cabinet size of 600mm and has a fully reversible drainer. A polished chrome basket strainer waste is also included. Reginox ceramics offer a stylish contemporary or traditional alternative to other materials. With many different styles available to choose from Reginox ceramics offer something to suit all kitchens.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">Supplied with a stylish Reginox Genesis modern kitchen tap and a polished chrome basket strainer waste.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px;\">This great looking sink comes with a 10 year manufacturers guarantee.</span><br></p>', 320, 319, '0.3125', 'Reginox Contemporary White Ceramic 1.0 Bowl Kitchen Sink RL504CW + Tap_1559544721.jpg', '0', NULL, '2019-06-03 04:52:01', '2019-06-03 04:52:01'),
