(430, 31, NULL, 0, 'Elite Showerhead', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 91, 89); font-family: nobel, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Super slim and uber stylish, transform your shower with Elite; a superior design offering a choice of 3 multifunctional spray settings to match a variety of showering needs for the ultimate feel-good experience. Each water flow channel has its own water supply, which means Elite can also conserve water when switched to a reduced flow setting.</span><br></p>', 650, 629, '3.230769230769231', 'FH2000UC_1_w635_h476_1559623614.jpg', '1', NULL, '2019-06-04 02:46:54', '2019-06-04 02:47:50'),
