(624, 44, NULL, 0, 'Ideal Standard Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Traditional Kitchen Sink', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The traditional deep design of the Belfast ceramic single bowl sink from Ideal Standard is the perfect choice for any kitchen, with the generously sized bowl giving plenty of room for your pots and pans.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Belfast sink is made from heavy duty fireclay. Fireclay is an extremely hard-wearing material, making it perfect for use in a busy kitchen as it’s resistant to acids, alkalis and staining meaning it maintains its pristine appearance and surface finish for a product life-time. It is also resistant to scratches, chipping and even heat- so you can place a hot pan down without worry of any damage.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The deep bowl guarantees durability and practicality, allowing of plenty of room for washing all of your plates and pans.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/belfast-sinks-420-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">Belfast sinks</a>&nbsp;have been a popular style of sink dating far back to the 1700’s due to the robust build and attractive design. The sink comes with a weir overflow to prevent overspill, preventing flooding by allowing water to drain away.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Ideal Standard Belfast Sink conforms to BS 1206:1974 and has a lifetime guarantee so you have important peace of mind.</span></p>', 280, 279, '0.35714285714285715', 'Ideal Standard Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Traditional Kitchen Sink_1559809983.png', '0', NULL, '2019-06-06 06:33:03', '2019-06-06 06:33:03'),
