(626, 44, NULL, 0, 'Reginox Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Kitchen Sink - Basket Strainer Waste Included', NULL, '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The unique and deep design of the Belfast ceramic single bowl sink from Reginox is the perfect purchase for anyone who uses their kitchen daily. By introducing this sink into your home, you\'ll&nbsp;be bringing home a timeless, country vibe with&nbsp;the single, generously sized bowl measuring&nbsp;an impressive 250mm in height, providing room for even the largest of pans.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">The Belfast sink is made from a traditional ceramic material which has a smooth,&nbsp;glazed look. Ceramic is an extremely hard wearing material, making it perfect for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/kitchen-sinks-78-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">kitchen sinks</a>&nbsp;as it’s resistant to scratches, staining and chipping, you can even put a hot pan straight down on it and you won’t need to worry about it getting damaged!</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Belfast&nbsp;sinks are largely found in traditional style kitchens and have been a popular style of sink dating far back to the 1700’s! The strong aesthetic appeals and robust build have clearly stayed in fashion over the years. The deep bowl guarantees durability and reliability, allowing of plenty of room for washing larger items.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://www.plumbworld.co.uk/belfast-sinks-420-0000\" class=\"auto_inserted\" style=\"color: inherit;\">Belfast sinks</a>&nbsp;are sometimes referred to as ‘London Sinks’ because they were first range of sinks to include an overflow. An overflow helps to prevent overspill, allowing water to drain away without the risk of flooding.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">To ensure a long and hassle-free life, these Reginox sinks come&nbsp;complete with a brilliant 10-year guarantee.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Features and benefits:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><li>Single bowl design</li><li>Belfast style</li><li>Waste included</li><li>No tap holes</li><li>An extremely hard wearing and robust ceramic build</li><li>Resistant to scratches, chipping and staining</li><li>Deep bowl</li><li>Complete with Basket strainer waste and overflow</li><li>10 year manufacturers guarantee</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">*Please note that waste disposal units cannot be fitted to this sink.</p>', 149, 143, '4.026845637583892', 'Reginox Belfast Ceramic Large Single Bowl Kitchen Sink - Basket Strainer Waste Included_1559810068.png', '0', NULL, '2019-06-06 06:34:29', '2019-06-06 06:34:29'),
